Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.37,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.59,Default,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.62,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.63,Default,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:43.67,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:44.43,Default,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.59,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
